description.en:
We are building the first decentralized gaming ecosystem where you don't only play & earn, but own the games

GAME ONE goal is to unlock a new stream of revenues and enable players to earn money while playing.

they are not just players, but also game owners: They own the games of gameone porftolio by being members of the gameone dao.

How game one unlocks revenue stream for players?

players earn money on the gameone ecosystem with:

1. jackpots & prizes

2. multi-player Tournaments & battle rewards

3. Mobile game ads benefits sharing (On ios & android)
